'''''Most Precious Weapon''''' was the second [[Hasbro]]/[[Toys "R" Us]]&ndash;exclusive [[Star Wars comic books|comic]] published in [[2002]].

==Plot summary==
[[Count/Legends|Count]] [[Dooku/Legends|Dooku]] is meditating in his [[Solar sailer|Solar Sailer]]. He takes out his [[Lightsaber/Legends|lightsaber]] and remembers his training with [[Jedi Master/Legends|Jedi Master]] [[Yoda/Legends|Yoda]]. He contemplates how his former master's advice helped him in his [[First Battle of Geonosis/Legends|duel]] with [[Anakin Skywalker/Legends|Anakin Skywalker]] and [[Obi-Wan Kenobi/Legends|Obi-Wan Kenobi]].

